##곰페르츠 모수추정 mle (b)

mgom_non<-function(data,c) {   
x<-data$Midage 

y<-data$Nonsmokers.death.
n<-data$ Nonsmokers.pop.

p<-1-exp( -exp(c[1]+c[2]*x) ) # gompit link function        
p<-as.numeric(p)

  -sum(dbinom(y,n,p,log=TRUE))  
}

mle_gom_non<-optim(c(-5,0),mgom_non, data=cig, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)
mle_gom_non$par         ## -5.62248037  0.05898679
## [1] -5.62248037  0.05898679
mgom_cig<-function(data,c) {   
x<-data$Midage 

y<-data$Cigarette.only.death.
n<-data$Cigarette.only.pop.

p<-1-exp( -exp(c[1]+c[2]*x) ) # gompit link function        
p<-as.numeric(p)

  -sum(dbinom(y,n,p,log=TRUE))  
}

mle_gom_cig<-optim(c(-5,0),mgom_cig, data=cig, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)
mle_gom_cig$par         ##  -5.91405416  0.07098122
## [1] -5.91405416  0.07098122
###두 방법 모두 비슷한 값이 나왔는데 mle의 경우, 미리 구한, 최소 추정치를 이용하기 때문에 ols보다좀 더 정확했다. 하지만,ols방법은 mle 방법보다 쉽게 이용할 수 있다는 것이 장점이었다. 

##생명표(c)
lx_ftn<-function(a,b){
t<-seq(5,70,by=5)
x<-20
10^5*exp(-exp(a+b*x)*(exp(b*t)-1)/b)
} 
lx_non<-lx_ftn(-5.62248037,  0.05898679)  ## -5.62248037  0.05898679
lx_cig<-lx_ftn(-5.91405416, 0.07098122)##  -5.91405416  0.07098122
lx_non<-c(100000,lx_non) #x=20일 때 값 추가
lx_cig<-c(100000,lx_cig)

lxplus<-function(x,a,b){
t<-1:100
sum(10^5*exp(-exp(a+b*x)*(exp(b*t)-1)/b))
} 
ex_non<-rep(0,15) #0벡터 지정

## mle, 모수추정(c)

dgumbel<-function(y,mu,sigma){
  -exp((y-mu)/sigma)-exp((y-mu)/sigma)/sigma
}

dgompertz<-function(y,mu,sigma){
  exp((y-mu)/sigma)-exp((y-mu)/sigma)/sigma
}

pgompertz<-function(y,mu,sigma){
  1-exp(-exp((y-mu)/sigma))
}


mle_wei2<- function(data,par) {                       #2p weibull mle
mu<-par[1];   sigma<-par[2];  
y<- data$ymiles
y<-as.numeric(y)
y<-log(y,exp(1))

-sum(log(dgompertz(y, mu, sigma),exp(1)))
}

mle_wei3<- function(data,par) {                       #3p weibull mle
mu<-par[1];   sigma<-par[2];  a<-par[3]
y<- data$ymiles
y<-as.numeric(y)
y<-log(y-a,exp(1))

-sum(log(dgompertz(y,mu,sigma),exp(1)))
}

mle_lognorm <- function(data,par) {                  #lognormal mle
mu<-par[1];   sigma<-par[2];  
y<- data$ymiles
y<-as.numeric(y)
y<-log(y,exp(1))

-sum(log(dnorm(y,mean=mu,sd=sigma),exp(1)))
}

mle_gom<-function(data,par) {                            #gompertz mle
            
mu<-par[1];   sigma<-par[2];  
y<- data$ymiles
y<-as.numeric(y)

-sum(log(dgompertz(y, mu, sigma),exp(1)))   
}

mle_gum<-function(data,par) {                            #gumbel mle
            
mu<-par[1];   sigma<-par[2];  
y<- data$ymiles
y<-as.numeric(y)

-sum(dgumbel(y, mu, sigma))
}

mle_norm <- function(data,par) {                  #normal mle
mu<-par[1];   sigma<-par[2];  
y<- data$ymiles
y<-as.numeric(y)

-sum(log(dnorm(y,mean=mu,sd=sigma),exp(1)))
}

result1_wei2<-optim(c(10000,10000), mle_wei2, data=loco, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)
result1_wei3<-optim(c(10000,10000,0), mle_wei3, data= loco, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)        
result1_lognorm<-optim(c(1000,100), mle_lognorm, data= loco, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)        
result1_gom<-optim(c(10000,10000), mle_gom, data= loco, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)        
result1_gum<-optim(c(1000,1000), mle_gum, data= loco, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)
result1_norm<-optim(c(10000,10000), mle_norm, data= loco, method= "BFGS", hessian=T)

## 최적 선형모형 추정 (a)

###xp를 자료 순서대로 했을 경우

hp1<-lm(Stature~Humerus,data=wom)
hp2<-lm(Stature~Humerus+Radius,data=wom)
hp3<-lm(Stature~Humerus+Radius+Ulna,data=wom)
hp4<-lm(Stature~Humerus+Radius+Ulna+Femur,data=wom)
hp5<-lm(Stature~Humerus+Radius+Ulna+Femur+Tibia,data=wom)
hp6<-lm(Stature~Humerus+Radius+Ulna+Femur+Tibia+Fibula,data=wom)
n0<-40


var_h1<- sum(hp1$residuals^2)/40
var_h2<- sum(hp2$residuals^2)/40
var_h3<- sum(hp3$residuals^2)/40
var_h4<- sum(hp4$residuals^2)/40
var_h5<- sum(hp5$residuals^2)/40
var_h6<- sum(hp6$residuals^2)/40


lftn<-function(n0,var){
pi<-3.1415
(-n0/2)*log(2*pi*var)-n0/2
}                                      #log likelihood ftn

aicftn<-function(p,n0,var){
(-2)*lftn(n0,var)+2*(p+2)
}                                       #AIC ftn

aic_1<-(-2)*aicftn(1,n0,var_h1)
aic_2<-(-2)*aicftn(2,n0,var_h2)
aic_3<-(-2)*aicftn(3,n0,var_h3)
aic_4<-(-2)*aicftn(4,n0,var_h4)
